text:
Name: Heather Hester.
Graduation Year: 2024.
Description: Heather Hester is a dedicated Biomedical Science student with a strong passion for innovation and learning. Throughout their academic journey, they have gained experience in biomedical science research and practical applications. They aspire to become a musician producing compositions for films and media. Their dedication to excellence and problem-solving skills make them a promising professional in their field..
